OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FCounter-terror police are looking into
OL,7,Fwhether a series of arson attacks
OL,8,Fagainst Jewish sites in north London
OL,9,Fhave been carried out by Iranian
OL,10,Fproxies.
OL,12,FPremises linked to people opposing the
OL,13,FIranian regime have also been
OL,14,Ftargeted, the deputy commissioner of
OL,15,Fthe Metropolitan Police has said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FVicki Evans, deputy assistant
OL,7,Fcommissioner of the force, said most
OL,8,Fhave been claimed online by Harakat
OL,9,FAshab al-Yamin al-Islamia, the Islamic
OL,10,FMovement of the Companions of the
OL,11,FRight.
OL,13,F` March 23:
OL,15,FFour Jewish community ambulances were
OL,16,Ftorched in Golders Green, north-west
OL,17,FLondon, in the early hours.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FThe vehicles were from Hatzola, a
OL,7,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,8,Foperating in the area, and
OL,9,Finvestigators have probed claims that
OL,10,FHarakat Ashab al-Yamin al-Islamia was
OL,11,Fbehind the attack.
OL,13,FA video was posted on Telegram
OL,14,Ffeaturing a map of the location where
OL,15,Fthe ambulances were kept and footage
OL,16,Fof them on fire.
OL,18,FSince the alleged attack, four males
OL,19,Fhave been charged over the incident.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FTwo British men, Hamza Iqbal, 20, and
OL,7,FRehan Khan, 19, from Leyton, east
OL,8,FLondon, and a 17-year-old boy, of dual
OL,9,FBritish-Pakistani nationality, from
OL,10,FWalthamstow, were charged with arson
OL,11,Fbeing reckless as to whether life
OL,12,Fwould be endangered.
OL,14,FThey were remanded in custody earlier
OL,15,Fthis month.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FOn Saturday, Judex Atshatshi, 18, a
OL,7,FBritish national from Dagenham, east
OL,8,FLondon, appeared at Westminster
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court charged with arson
OL,10,Fwith intent to damage property and
OL,11,Fbeing reckless as to whether life
OL,12,Fwould be endangered. He was also
OL,13,Fremanded in custody.
OL,15,FThe four defendants are set to appear
OL,16,Fat the Old Bailey on April 24.
OL,18,F` April 15:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FAttempted arson attacks are carried
OL,7,Fout in the early hours at Finchley
OL,8,FReform Synagogue, and at about 8.30pm
OL,9,Foutside the offices of a Persian media
OL,10,Fcompany, both in north-west London.
OL,12,FBottles, one thought to contain
OL,13,Fpetrol, were placed near the synagogue
OL,14,Fin Fallow Court Avenue, Finchley.
OL,16,FTwo people wearing dark clothing and
OL,17,Fbalaclavas were seen approaching the
OL,18,Fbuilding and neither of the bottles
OL,19,Fwere ignited, the Metropolitan Police
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FThey fled the scene with no damage or
OL,7,Finjuries reported, it added.
OL,9,FThat evening, the Met police announced
OL,10,Fit had arrested a 47-year-old woman
OL,11,Fand a 46-year-old man on suspicion of
OL,12,Farson endangering life in connection
OL,13,Fwith the incident.
OL,15,FIt said the woman was arrested at an
OL,16,Faddress in Watford and the 46-year-old
OL,17,Fman was arrested in the Watford area.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
