OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FHours after the alleged attack in
OL,7,FFinchley, an "ignited container" was
OL,8,Fthrown towards the site of Volant
OL,9,FMedia, the parent company of Persian
OL,10,Fnews channel Iran International.
OL,12,FIt landed in a car park where the fire
OL,13,Fimmediately went out.
OL,15,FThere were no injuries and the
OL,16,Fsuspects left the area in a black four-
OL,17,Fwheel-drive vehicle, police have said.
OL,19,FThree people were charged with arson
OL,20,Fwith intent to endanger life after the
OL,21,Fincident in north-west London.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
