FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FOisin McGuinness, 21, Nathan Dunn, 19,
OL,7,Fand a 16-year-old boy appeared at
OL,8,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,9,FFriday where they spoke only to
OL,10,Fconfirm their personal details.
OL,12,FThe boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,13,Freasons, was remanded to the care of a
OL,14,Flocal authority with conditions and
OL,15,Fwill next appear at the Old Bailey on
OL,16,FMay 15 for a preliminary hearing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
