OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FMcGuinness and Dunn, both of Watford,
OL,7,Fwere each ordered to next appear in
OL,8,Fcustody at the Old Bailey for a pre-
OL,9,Ftrial preparation hearing on the same
OL,10,Fdate.J` April 18:
OL,12,FItems were found near the Israeli
OL,13,Fembassy, central London, in the
OL,14,Fmorning, and that night a former
OL,15,FJewish charity building was attacked
OL,16,Fin Hendon, Barnet.
OL,18,FA man was spotted approaching the row
OL,19,Fof shops carrying a plastic bag later
OL,20,Ffound to contain three bottles of
OL,21,Ffluid, police said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
