FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FHe placed the bag by the old Jewish
OL,7,FFutures building before lighting the
OL,8,Fitems inside and fleeing after they
OL,9,Ffailed to fully ignite, police added.
OL,11,FThe shopfront sustained minor damage
OL,12,Fand no injuries were reported.
OL,14,FA video, which appears to have been
OL,15,Fshared by Harakat Ashab al-Yamin al-
OL,16,FIslamia, shows a target over an image
OL,17,Fof the Israeli embassy and people
OL,18,Fdressed in hazmat suits flying drones.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
