PN,40912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FAnother apparent Harakat Ashab al-
OL,7,FYamin al-Islamia clip claimed the
OL,8,FHendon attack.
OL,10,F` April 19:
OL,12,FA "bottle with some sort of
OL,13,Faccelerant" is "thrown through the
OL,14,Fwindow" of Kenton United Synagogue,
OL,15,FHarrow, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,17,FSmoke was seen inside a room at the
OL,18,Fsynagogue after officers spotted
OL,19,Fdamage to the window at around
OL,20,Fmidnight.
OL,26,@tD@COUuD@KO]uD@POUvD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
