OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776767959
OL,3,CTimeline of spate of arson attacks
OL,4,Cagainst Jewish sites in London
OL,6,FVideo that seems to be from Harakat
OL,7,FAshab al-Yamin al-Islamia shows a
OL,8,Fperson in dark clothing lighting an
OL,9,Fitem and throwing it at the synagogue
OL,10,Fbefore running away.
OL,12,FTwo teenagers, a 17-year-old boy and a
OL,13,F19-year-old man, have since been
OL,14,Farrested in connection with the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the Met Police said
OL,18,Fon Monday morning that the pair remain
OL,19,Fin custody.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
